    <item>
      <title>据《Kini》报道，斯沃琪在马来西亚因彩虹节扣押手表而胜诉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/swatch-wins-malaysia-suit-over-pride-watch-seizure-kini-reports</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据《当今大马》报道，瑞士手表制造商斯沃琪集团 (Swatch Group AG) 赢得了对马来西亚政府的诉讼，该诉讼涉及去年在东南亚国家扣押其以同志骄傲为主题的手表，引发了争议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/swatch-wins-malaysia-suit-over-pride-watch-seizure-kini-reports</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Nov 2024 02:27:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>流动性紧张之际，万达寻求延长 4 亿美元债券发行期限</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/wanda-seeks-to-extend-400-million-bond-amid-liquidity-strains</link>
      <description><![CDATA[大连万达商业管理集团股份有限公司旗下一家子公司提议对其 2025 年到期的美元债券制定新的条款以延长其期限，此举反映出该中国公司在中国房地产市场低迷时期面临的流动性挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/wanda-seeks-to-extend-400-million-bond-amid-liquidity-strains</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Nov 2024 02:24:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国连续第二个月维持政策性贷款利率不变</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/china-keeps-policy-loan-rate-unchanged-for-second-month</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国央行在 9 月份下调政策贷款利率后，此次维持其不变，表明当局在加大货币刺激力度方面保持耐心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/china-keeps-policy-loan-rate-unchanged-for-second-month</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Nov 2024 01:50:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>股票、债券价格因交易员青睐 Bessent 而上涨：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-24/dollar-falls-as-treasury-pick-tempers-trump-bets-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[股票和国债价格上涨，交易员对唐纳德·特朗普选择斯科特·贝森特担任财政部长表示欢迎，认为这一慎重选择将为美国经济和金融市场注入更多稳定性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-24/dollar-falls-as-treasury-pick-tempers-trump-bets-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 24 Nov 2024 22:39:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>比特币涨势在接近历史性 10 万美元水平后停滞</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-24/bitcoin-s-btc-rally-stalls-after-nearing-the-historic-100-000-level</link>
      <description><![CDATA[比特币一度上涨至 10 万美元，但在接近历史水平后回落，随后趋于稳定，交易员正在评估当选总统唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 对加密货币的支持所带来的乐观情绪是否变得过分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-24/bitcoin-s-btc-rally-stalls-after-nearing-the-historic-100-000-level</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 24 Nov 2024 22:00:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普的财政部选择推动全球救援货币兑美元上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-24/dollar-s-sizzling-rally-cools-as-bessent-nominated-for-treasury</link>
      <description><![CDATA[斯科特·贝森特 (Scott Bessent) 当选为下一任财政部长推动了全球货币的上涨，因为交易员们减少了对唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 回归将引发全球市场震动的押注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-24/dollar-s-sizzling-rally-cools-as-bessent-nominated-for-treasury</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 24 Nov 2024 21:45:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
